Von Essen Hotels Is Close to Being Sold, E&Y Says, Mail Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-15T17:28:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/von-essen-hotels-is-close-to-being-sold-e-y-says-mail-reports.html
Von Essen Hotels Ltd., the chain of
26 hotels founded in 1998, will be sold within a month,
administrators Ernst & Young LLP said, the Mail on Sunday
reported. Ernst & Young has already been approached by
interested property groups and hoteliers, the Mail said, without
citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 